    "en": {
      "title": "Four countries will stop receiving mail",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Postmaster General Ranjith Ariyaratne Masahatha informs that due to the restriction and suspension of flights to Sri Lanka due to the existing fuel crisis, the acceptance of postal items to 4 countries has been suspended until further notice.",
        "Accordingly, the acceptance of postal items to the United States of America, the Netherlands, Israel and Russia has been suspended.",
        "In addition to this, he further announced that postal transport within the country has been delayed due to difficulty in providing fuel."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "Four",
